{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"c5ca337ac1","title":"春雷（诗）","origin":"《四川省右派言论选辑10》（内部文件，只供领导同志参考，请勿外传和翻印），中共四川省委宣传部办公室编，1957年9月5日。","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"d69ca5da8b","index":0,"year":1957,"month":5,"day":null,"articleId":"c5ca337ac1"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-fanyou","name":"中国反右运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"368edbb40d","name":"李加建"},{"id":"a185c9b36c","name":"四川"}]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-fanyou":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"05d5ffc1aa","type":"title","text":"春雷（诗）","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"c5ca337ac1"},{"id":"87ede9a611","type":"authors","text":"四川李加建","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"c5ca337ac1"},{"id":"3d5daef764","type":"paragraph","text":"(注：今年一月，成都展开对〈草木篇〉的批判后，李加建曾受石天河的指使，在自贡积极组织支持〈草木篇〉的文章和讨论会，后李见大势已去，在极端仇恨的心情下，写了这首诗，寄给石天河，企图在《星星》上发表，未果。)","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"c5ca337ac1"},{"id":"732657c666","type":"paragraph","text":"春雷从大海那儿取得声音，从太阳那儿取得光和热，滚滚压地而来。","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"c5ca337ac1"},{"id":"8d67d683c5","type":"paragraph","text":"它对着坚硬的冰山、厚实的雪原，灰云密布的天空，爆炸了自己。","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"c5ca337ac1"},{"id":"67419d7359","type":"paragraph","text":"在雷声隆隆的回荡中，冰山崩裂，雪原溶化，灰云飞灭，而柔嫩的新芽冒出头来，蜷缩的蓓蕾继开花瓣，枯枝上冲出片片新叶儿……","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"c5ca337ac1"},{"id":"e53c6e1022","type":"paragraph","text":"震天雷声，并无损于幼嫩的、新的出生，却成了它们的催生者，它宣布了那些貌若磐石的，老朽的死亡！","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"c5ca337ac1"},{"id":"1229196eaf","type":"paragraph","text":"雷声滚到我心上，使我一惊！但我高兴，它挥落了昨日留在我心上的灰尘！","index":7,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"c5ca337ac1"}],"page":{"id":"bd5fc4f805","publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"c5ca337ac1","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}